Package: varma
Type: Package
Title: Tools for Vector Autoregressive Moving-Average (VARMA) Model Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Matteo", "Pelagatti",
      email = "matteo.pelagatti@unimib.it",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: Provides a comprehensive suite of functions for multivariate time
    series analysis using Vector Autoregressive Moving-Average (VARMA)
    models. The package supports model specification, parameter estimation,
    statistical inference, bootstrapping, and diagnostic checking.
    Core computational routines are implemented in C++ via 'Rcpp' for performance.
License: GPL (>= 3)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
